{
  "title": "暗里着迷",
  "title_raw": "暗里着迷",
  "version": null,
  "artist": "刘德华",
  "group_key": "暗里着迷|刘德华",
  "writers": {
    "lyricist": "林振强",
    "composer": "徐嘉良",
    "arranger": null
  },
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "time": 23.0,
      "time_str": "00:23.000",
      "text": "可不可不要这么样  徘徊在目光内",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 30.0,
      "time_str": "00:30.000",
      "text": "你会察觉到我根本寂寞难耐",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 111.0,
      "time_str": "01:51.000",
      "text": "[00:38]即使千多百个深夜  曾在梦境内",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 118.0,
      "time_str": "01:58.000",
      "text": "[00:44]我有吻过你  这毕竟并没存在",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 126.0,
      "time_str": "02:06.000",
      "text": "[00:52]人声车声开始消和逝",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 129.0,
      "time_str": "02:09.000",
      "text": "[00:55]无声挣扎有个情感奴隶",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 133.0,
      "time_str": "02:13.000",
      "text": "[00:59]是我多么的想她",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 135.0,
      "time_str": "02:15.000",
      "text": "[01:02]但我偏偏只得无尽叹谓",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 162.0,
      "time_str": "02:42.000",
      "text": "[01:28]共我道别吧  别让空虚使我越轨",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 169.0,
      "time_str": "02:49.000",
      "text": "[02:20][01:06]其实每次见你我也着迷",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 173.0,
      "time_str": "02:53.000",
      "text": "[02:24][01:10]无奈你我各有角色范围",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 177.0,
      "time_str": "02:57.000",
      "text": "[02:27][01:14]就算在寂寞梦内超出好友关系",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 184.0,
      "time_str": "03:04.000",
      "text": "[02:35][01:21]唯在暗里爱你暗里着迷",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 188.0,
      "time_str": "03:08.000",
      "text": "[02:38][01:25]无谓要你惹上各种问题",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 192.0,
      "time_str": "03:12.000",
      "text": "共我道别吧  就让空虚把我摧毁",
      "translation": null
    }
  ],
  "has_translation": false,
  "source_file": "暗里着迷 - 刘德华.lrc"
}